Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.16,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k316}Did you hear about Google's latest AI announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:04.67,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k151}It's pretty incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.46,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k178}Oh, really? What's new?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:09.06,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k260}Another language model or something similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.25,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k119}Even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:14.33,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k408}They've unveiled a new AI model called Gemini TTS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:17.94,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k360}that can generate incredibly realistic human speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.14,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k219}Wow, realistic speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:21.89,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k175}That's a significant leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.48,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k158}What exactly can it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:27.14,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k366}Apparently, it can synthesize voices for different speakers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:30.10,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k296}and even generate audio in multiple languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:33.00,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k289}Experts are genuinely impressed by the quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:36.70,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k370}That sounds amazing for things like audio books or voice assistants,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:39.64,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k293}but I can't help but think about potential downsides.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:40.43,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k79}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:43.47,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k303}Some experts are raising concerns about misuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:47.07,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k360}The potential for creating deep fakes or spreading misinformation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.67,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k160}is definitely a worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.57,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k189}That's exactly what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:54.14,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k356}It's always a double-edged sword with these powerful new technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:56.32,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k217}The ethical implications are huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:57.43,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k111}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:00.07,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k264}It's part of Google's bigger push in AI,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:01.78,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k170}and while the tech is impressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:05.18,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k340}the conversation around responsible use will be critical.
